data.description: Gorgeously recently updated 3 bedroom 2 bath in lovely Cutler Bay. Just move in everything is done to perfection. Impact glass windows and doors, neutral colors throughout. White Shaker wood cabinets and light quartz counters opens to the family room looking over patio and back yard. Stainless steel appliances. Large covered back porch perfect for entertaining.    Corner home with new plumbing and oversized one car garage.  Close to great shopping, fine dining, Deering Estate park, Thalatta and library. A pleasure to show. Washer and dryer hook up in garage.
